ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisAppointment of GREG KLASSEN of Vancouver, British Columbia, to be President of the Canadian Tourism Commission on an interim basis, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, or until such time as a new President is appointed, whichever is earlier, effective April 1, 2014.
